</figDesc> 
</figure> 
 
is to fulfill a promise 3 years <lb> 
old,  I thought I would like to <lb> 
wind up with an obituary <lb> 
with the right amount of <orig reg="nonsense">non- <lb> 
sense</orig> in it.</p> 
 
<closer> 
<salute>Truly yours,</salute> 
<signed>SL Clemens</signed> 
</closer> 
</div1> 
   
